      },
      "writtenOn": "2016-04-01T18:06:52Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "kIPv4 is really a bit-flag indicating we really want to bind to an IPv4 interface. If this fails, there is no point in trying an IPv6 one too.",
      "parentUuid": "2ec1e019_6d8335cb",
