      "writtenOn": "2016-04-01T18:17:25Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "what if ipv4 is completely disabled on the box? I would expect this first call to fail, but if mode was ipv4|ipv6 and we tried v6, we would succeed there",
      "parentUuid": "6e0e782a_7a6d3501",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 121,
